evrouter|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
evrouter: evrouter (An input layer event router for Linux)
evrouter:
evrouter: Evrouter reads events from the Linux input layer, and, based on a 
evrouter: user-specified set of rules, acts on them. Currently, evrouter can map
evrouter: events to X11 key and button presses, XMMS commands, and can also run
evrouter: shell  commands.
evrouter:
evrouter: http://www.bedroomlan.org/projects/evrouter
